org.osmdroid.samplefragments.drawing

Class PressToPlot

  • java.lang.Object
    • Fragment
      • org.osmdroid.samplefragments.BaseSampleFragment
        • org.osmdroid.samplefragments.drawing.PressToPlot
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PressToPlotWithoutWrapping

    public class PressToPlot
extends BaseSampleFragment
    A simple sample to plot markers with a long press. It's a bit of noise this in the class that is used to help the osmdroid devs troubleshoot things. Map replication is ON for this sample (only viewable for numerically lower zoom levels (higher altitude)) created on 11/19/2017.
    Since:
    6.0.0
